            . I am a pawnbroker. I have a pillow pawned by the female prisoner for 1s., on the 25th of January.</p>
               <p>JAMES HARRIS. I have a pillow and sheet pawned on the 23rd of January by the man - he said they were his own.</p>
               <p>JOHN HAMFORTH. The two prisoners were brought to me at the watch-house; the woman told me where the duplicates were, and I found them behind the stove.</p>
